quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  108,1,"Muvugishwamana! Mu vy’ukuri, Twarakweguriye impano y’ivyiza vyinshi nta ngere kw’isi no mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  108,2,"Kubera ivyo rero, senga wamizeko wongere ukerere kw’izina ry’Imana no ku bw’Imana yawe Rurema Allah."
  108,3,"Mu vy’ukuri, uwugucokora akanka n’uburongozi warungikanwe, ni we yacitswe n’ivyiza vyose, kw’isi no mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
